<div class="wpb-alert style-yellow">

<p>üö®<strong>Note: </strong>WP Simple Pay has a <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/stripe" target="_blank" title="WP Simple Pay - Free Stripe Plugin for WordPress">free version</a>, but you‚Äôll need the Pro plan to unlock the Bacs Direct Debit payment template.</p>

</div>


<p>Next, you need to install and activate the <a href="https://wpsimplepay.com" target="_blank" title="WP Simple Pay - WordPress Payments Plugin">WP Simple Pay</a> plugin. For detailed instructions, see our tutorial on <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/" title="How to Install a WordPress Plugin ‚Äì Step by Step for Beginners">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>



<p>Upon activation, the setup wizard will automatically launch on your screen. Here, you have to click the ‚ÄòLet‚Äôs Get Started‚Äô button.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="297" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepaywizard.png" alt="The WP Simple Pay Setup Wizard Will Start Automatically" class="wp-image-119509" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepaywizard.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepaywizard-300x131.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>This will take you to the next step, where you need to enter your license key.</p>



<p>You can find this information in your account on the WP Simple Pay website. Entering it will unlock the pro features required to accept Bacs Direct Debit payments.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="365" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayactivatelicense.png" alt="You‚Äôll Be Asked to Enter Your WP Simple Pay License Key" class="wp-image-119510" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayactivatelicense.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayactivatelicense-300x161.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<h5 class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Connect to Stripe</h5>



<p>After that, you‚Äôll be asked to connect your site with Stripe. </p>



<p>Since WP Simple Pay is a Stripe-powered plugin, it won‚Äôt work until you connect it with a Stripe account. If you don‚Äôt already have one, you can create a new Stripe account during this process.</p>



<p>Stripe is what makes the Direct Debit work in the background. Unlike card payments, Bacs takes a few working days for the money to move from your customer‚Äôs bank.</p>



<p>Once Stripe is connected, WP Simple Pay takes care of everything. For more details, check our step-by-step guide on <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-accept-payments-with-stripe-in-wordpress/" title="How to Accept Payments with Stripe in WordPress">accepting Stripe payments in WordPress</a>.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="345" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Connect-with-Stripe-1-1.png" alt="Connect with Stripe" class="wp-image-227268" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Connect-with-Stripe-1-1.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Connect-with-Stripe-1-1-300x152.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<h5 class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Configure WP Simple Pay Settings</h5>



<p>Next, the wizard will guide you to set up your email notifications. Here you can enable options to receive email notifications for payment receipts, upcoming invoices, and payment notifications.</p>



<p>You can also choose the email address where you want to receive these notifications.</p>



<p>When you‚Äôre finished, click &#8216;Save and Continue&#8217; to move to the final setup steps.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="432" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayemail.png" alt="Configure Your WP Simple Pay Emails" class="wp-image-119512" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayemail.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/applepayemail-300x191.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<h5 class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Create a Bacs Direct Debit Payment Form</h5>



<p>At this point, WP Simple Pay will finish configuring your site, and you‚Äôll be ready to create your Bacs Direct Debit payment form.</p>



<p>For this, head over to the <strong>WP Simple Pay ¬ª Payment Forms</strong> page from your WordPress dashboard and click the &#8216;Create Your Payment Form&#8217; button.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="332" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/click-create-your-payment-form-button.png" alt="Click Create your Payment form button" class="wp-image-319923" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/click-create-your-payment-form-button.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/click-create-your-payment-form-button-300x146.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>This will take you to the template library. </p>



<p>WP Simple Pay gives you plenty of premade templates, but since we‚Äôre focusing on Direct Debit, go ahead and select the &#8216;Bacs Direct Debit Form&#8217; template.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="348" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-bacs-direct-debit-form-template.png" alt="Choose the Bacs Direct Debit form template in WP Simple Pay" class="wp-image-366674" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-bacs-direct-debit-form-template.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-bacs-direct-debit-form-template-300x154.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>Once you‚Äôve done that, you‚Äôll land on the &#8216;Add New Payment Form&#8217; page. </p>



<p>Here you can add a title and description for your form. I suggest keeping these short and clear since your customers will see them during checkout. </p>



<p>With the basics in place, make sure the form type is set to &#8216;On-site payment form.&#8217; This ensures your customers can finish checkout without leaving your site. </p>



<p>If you want to add a bit more protection, I also recommend checking the &#8216;Spam &amp; Fraud Protection&#8217; box. It adds a <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-add-captcha-in-wordpress-login-and-registration-form/" title="How to Add CAPTCHA in WordPress Login and Registration Form">CAPTCHA to your form</a>, protecting it from malicious bots.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="360" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-title-and-description-for-bacs-direct-debit-form-in-wpsimplepay.png" alt="Add title and description for Bacs direct debit form in WP Simple Pay" class="wp-image-366676" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-title-and-description-for-bacs-direct-debit-form-in-wpsimplepay.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-title-and-description-for-bacs-direct-debit-form-in-wpsimplepay-300x159.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>Next, move over to the &#8216;Payment&#8217; tab on the left. This is where you‚Äôll set the price for your product or service. </p>



<p>If you‚Äôre offering a subscription, choose ‚ÄòSubscription‚Äô and click ‚ÄòAdd Price‚Äô. You can create multiple tiers, like a Basic Plan at ¬£10/month and a Premium Plan at ¬£20/month.</p>



<p>However, if you are just selling a single product and don&#8217;t need to set up recurring payments, you can choose the &#8216;One time&#8217; option and add your pricing.</p>



<p>At this stage, don‚Äôt forget to set your currency to &#8216;GBP&#8217;. </p>



<p>Bacs Direct Debit only works with British pounds. If you set a different currency, like USD or EUR, then payments won‚Äôt process correctly.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="311" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/configure-your-product-or-subscription-price-in-wpsimplepay.png" alt="Configure your product or subscription price in WP Simple Pay" class="wp-image-366678" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/configure-your-product-or-subscription-price-in-wpsimplepay.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/configure-your-product-or-subscription-price-in-wpsimplepay-300x137.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>As you scroll down, you‚Äôll see the &#8216;Payment Methods&#8217; section. Here, you need to make sure &#8216;Bacs Direct Debit&#8217; is selected.</p>



