<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Method 2: Accept Bacs Payments in WooCommerce With Manual Bank Transfers</h4>



<p>If you already run a <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/woocommerce-tutorial-ultimate-guide/" title="WooCommerce Made Simple: A Step-by-Step Tutorial [+ Resources]">WooCommerce store</a> and want to reach UK customers without extra plugins, then this method works well.</p>



<p>WooCommerce comes with a built-in Direct Bank Transfer option, which works perfectly for handling Bacs payments. Customers simply choose this option at checkout, send money directly to your bank account, and you confirm the payment on your end.</p>



<p>However, before I dive into the setup, it‚Äôs important to understand the trade-offs of this approach:</p>



