<li><strong>No automation:</strong> You have to check your bank account and manually mark each order as paid.</li>



<li><strong>Slower process for customers:</strong> Customers must leave your site to complete the payment through their online banking.</li>



<li><strong>Best for low volume:</strong> This works well if you only process a few orders per month, but it is not ideal for busy stores.</li>
